Crime Detection in Security Camera Footage

Dataset available at https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/odins0n/ucf-crime-dataset (Very large dataset, not included in this repo)
Easiest way to run: Notebooks directory contains the notebooks of 4 different models. Run these models in the Kaggle environment to achieve the same results.
Current Python files contain the 3CNN model. Run main.py to see results.
Models directory contains the weights of some fully trained models.
